ports login, registration, forgotten password and reset password. All these forms are AJAX powered, and in the template settings, you can disable registration or forgotten password forms. If you use forgotten password form, email generated by it will contain URL to the same login page to use reset password form. One thing that is custom done on Dev4Press.com now is that custom code is used to disable wp-login.php file, and redirect users to new login page.</p>\n<p>There are many other small updates to xScape, some external libraries are updated (FontAwesome icons and Smart Responsive Breadcrumbs), AJAX handling code is cleaned up and improved to handle different request types (more things will be done with AJAX in xScape in the future).</p>\n<p>If you notice any issues with the framework or themes, please let me know through support forums.</p>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/themes-news/xscape-framework-and-core-1-9-3/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:84:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/themes-news/xscape-framework-and-core-1-9-3/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"Development plans: July &amp; August 2013";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_exp