;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"updates";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"http://www.dev4press.com/?p=20840";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:259:"New major release for GD Press Tools Pro includes improvements to debugger and tracker, many updates, updated all jQuery libraries, refactored and updated JavaScript code, some fixes and changes, and plugin drops support for WordPress versions older then 3.3.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"MillaN";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1773:"<p>New major release for GD Press Tools Pro includes improvements to debugger and tracker, many updates, updated all jQuery libraries, refactored and updated JavaScript code, some fixes and changes, and plugin drops support for WordPress versions older then 3.3.</p>\n<p>GD Press Tools 4.5 Pro is tested with WordPress 3.6, and because of major jQuery update in this WordPress, all JavaScript code in GD Press Tools is refactored and updated. Because of that, plugin requires WordPress 3.3 or newer to work. All jQuery libraries in the plugin are updated to latest available stable versions. Our own gdr2 library is also updated. Plugin is tested with PHP 5.4 and some minor issues are fixed.</p>\n<p>Debugger has new panel for displaying log with executed hooks, and tracker is updated to track the hooks execution. Htaccess tweaks from <a href="http://perishablepress.com/5g-blacklist-2013/" target="_blank">PerishablePress</a> are updated to latest 5G versions. Plugin includes many small fixes and updates, including fixes to some problems with the backup.</p>\n<div class="xss-infobox xss-infobox-color-red"><strong>Important</strong>: GD Press Tools 4.5 Pro drops support for WordPress 3.0, 3.1 and 3.2. Minimum requirements for the plugin is: WordPress 3.3 or newer, PHP 5.2.4 or newer and mySQL 5.0 or newer.</div>\n<p>If you have any issues with this new version, please report them in the forums or in the comments here. As for the future releases of GD Press Tools Pro, there will be major changes coming to the plugin organization and more on that will be announced soon.</p>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/plugins-news/gd-press-tools-4-5-pro/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/plugins-news/gd-press-tools-4-5-pro/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:66:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:30:"All three Lite plugins updated";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/plugins-news/all-three-lite-plugins-updated/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lan