a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1618:"<p>Smart Responsive Breadcrumbs is NOT WordPress plugin, it is breadcrumbs navigation enhancer made with jQuery and CSS (with use of media queries), that comes with many color styles and many different effects that can be combined for best look for desktop and mobile browsers.</p>\n<p><a href="http://d4p.me/ccsrb"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-19892" alt="smart-responsive-breadcrumbs.preview" src="http://cdn.dev4press.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/smart-responsive-breadcrumbs.preview.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<p>Smart Responsive Breadcrumbs will be used for all future xScape based themes, including soon to be released skyScape. Plugin cost only <strong>$8.00</strong> and includes documentation,support (via CodeCanyon comments or official website forum). Official website contains a demo of the plugin in action.</p>\n<div class="xss-infobox xss-infobox-color-red"><h4>Smart Responsive Breadcrumbs:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>On Official Website: <a href="http://www.millan.rs/product/smart-responsive-breadcrumbs/" target="_blank">Smart Responsive Breadcrumbs</a></li>\n<li>On CodeCanyon: <a href="http://d4p.me/ccsrb" target="_blank">Smart Responsive Breadcrumbs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>SMART Plugins:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Official Website: <a href="http://www.millan.rs/" target="_blank">www.millan.rs</a></li>\n<li>On CodeCanyon: <a href="http://d4p.me/ccp" target="_blank">codecanyon.net</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/smart-plugins/smart-responsive-breadcrumbs/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:83:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/smart-plugins/smart-responsive-breadcrumbs/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explici