ses during the period, starting today and ending February 19 2013.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"MillaN";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2202:"<p>For the next 7 days, Dev4Press is having special promotion available for all purchase, giving big <strong>28%</strong> discount and some gifts for eligible purchases. Coupon is automatically applied to all purchases during the period, starting today and ending February 19 2013.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-19811" alt="vday_big" src="http://cdn.dev4press.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vday_big.png" width="560" height="128" /></p>\n<p>Discount coupon is automatically applied to all purchase links or cart checkout, but you can enter it manually during ShareIt side checkout for all new purchases. Coupon is: <strong>LOVEWEEK</strong>. Using this coupon you will get <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>28%</strong></span> discount for any purchase make between February 12 2013 to February 19 2013.</p>\n<p>Coupon can be used for any plugin, module or theme, for plugins pack or themes club membership or GD Star Rating support licenses. But, further more, some purchases will be eligible for additional gifts:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Purchase plugins pack (enterprise) and you will get <strong>3 themes </strong>and<strong> GD Star Rating Standard Support License</strong> for free.</li>\n<li>Purchase plugins pack (developer) and you will get <strong>2 themes</strong> for free.</li>\n<li>Purchase plugins pack (standard &#8211; subscription or lifetime) and you will get <strong>1 theme</strong> for free.</li>\n<li>Purchase any plugin (developer or enterprise) and you will get <strong>1 theme</strong> license for fre