ttribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"MillaN";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2227:"<p>With the first xScape based responsive theme coming soon, it is time to announce a new small project for creating the responsive menu with drop down capabilities, color styles, effects and easy to use mobile version. New menu will be part of all future xScape responsive themes.</p>\n<div id="attachment_19603" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 152px"><a title="Responsive Menu" href="http://cdn.dev4press.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/srm_test_responsive.png" rel="lightbox"><img class="wp-image-19603" title="Responsive Menu" alt="Responsive Menu" src="http://cdn.dev4press.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/srm_test_responsive-177x300.png" width="142" height="240" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Responsive Menu</p></div>\n<p>New menu project will be available with upcoming xScape themes, but if you want to buy it, it will be available from <a href="http://d4p.me/ccp" target="_blank">CodeCanyon</a> as a part of <a href="http://www.millan.rs/" target="_blank">SMART Plugins</a> project. It will be available there in the next 3-4 days. For now, here is a bit more info about new menu system.</p>\n<p>It will be in the form of jQuery plugin and set of CSS files split into smaller chunks for easier modification. Menu will have CSS file with some styling effects (transitions, shadows&#8230;), several different built in styles (each style in own file), mobile media queries (for different browser resolutions).</p>\n<p>Image on the right shows the menu for the smaller screen with vertical navigation. When on bigger screen, it will have a form of normal horizontal drop down menu:</p>\n<div id="attachment_19604" class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 474px"><a title="Normal Menu" href="http://cdn.dev4press.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/srm_test_one.png" rel="lightbox"><img class="wp-image-19604" title="Normal Menu" alt="Normal Menu" src="http://cdn.dev4press.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/srm_test_one-580x259.png" width="464" height="207" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Normal Menu</p></div>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/development/coming-soon-responsive-navigation-menu/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:91:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/development/coming-soon-responsive-navigation-menu/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:46;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:75:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:27:"Theme Coming Soon: skyScape";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/development/theme-coming-soon-skyscape/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:83:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/development/theme-coming-soon-skyscape/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";